divs: Sighting DetailsSighting Report: On May 19th, around 3p.m., I was entering the town that I live in and while I was turning to the first street on my right, I spotted something shiny in the sky. It was sunny and few clouds in the sky, I thought it was a plane but then I focused on the object and I could tell that it was moving fast and there was no wings like that of an airplane. I looked forward onto the road and looked up few seconds later and could not spot it again. It was oval and chrome to silver like color.
trends: There have been no other sightings in Warden
